author: johnh
msg: Support a fallback_url parameter in the content proxy. This URL is fetched when
the original target URL returns an error (HTTP >= 400).
This is of particular value with the image proxy: fallback_url can be set to a
valid known image to avoid broken images showing up.
Includes tweaks and a fix verified in integration test.
